{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_016", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王雪在出租车上捡到一个笔记本，里面写满了看不懂的符号。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "笔记本是国安局特工丢的，符号是加密情报。王雪因此被卷入了间谍案。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_017", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "公司前台新来的姑娘总是戴着一条围巾，即使在夏天也不摘。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "她脖子后面有一个特殊的纹身，是某个神秘组织的标志。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_018", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "李明家楼下的便利店每天凌晨三点都会有一辆黑色轿车停在门口。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "黑色轿车里的人在交易情报。便利店是某个地下情报站的中转点。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_019", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王雪的母亲临终前交给她一把钥匙，说以后会用上。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "钥匙打开了一家银行保险柜，里面是母亲年轻时的一本日记和一盒珠宝。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_020", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "公司的茶水间总有一个保温杯放在角落，但从没见过有人来拿。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "保温杯里藏着窃听器。有人通过它窃听公司高层的机密谈话。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_021", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "林悦在相亲时遇到一个男人，总觉得在哪里见过他。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "男人是她高中时的同桌，整容后换了身份回来找她。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_022", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "小区保安老张每天晚上都会在小区里巡逻三圈，雷打不动。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "low"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老张年轻时是特种兵，他在暗中保护小区里一个被黑帮盯上的证人。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_023", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "李明收到一封没有寄件人的快递，里面是一张照片——他十年前的旧居。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "有人在调查他的过去。照片背面有一行字：'你还记得那天的事吗？'", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_024", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王雪发现自己办公桌的抽屉被人翻过，但什么都没丢。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "翻抽屉的人是在找一份文件——那份文件被王雪无意中夹在了自己的笔记本里。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_025", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "公司楼下的咖啡店里总有一个老头坐在靠窗的位置，一坐就是一整天。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "low"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老头是退休的老刑警，他在监视对面楼里的一个嫌疑人。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_026", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "李明在地铁上遇到一个女孩，女孩戴着和他一模一样的项链。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那是他失散多年的妹妹。两人在孤儿院被分开收养，戴着同一对项链。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_027", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "赵峰的手机最近总是收到空白的短信，发件人不详。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "空白短信其实是摩斯密码的载体——有人用空格的长度编码了求救信息。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_028", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "小区里新搬来的住户从不和邻居说话，窗帘永远拉着。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "他是警方安插的卧底，正在调查小区里的一起连环失踪案。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_029", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王雪在旧货市场买了一台老式相机，里面的胶卷还没拍完。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "冲洗出来的照片记录了一场谋杀案的现场证据。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_030", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陈静的奶奶说家里有一个'传家宝'，但从不让任何人看。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "传家宝是一块唐代的免死金牌，是祖上当大官时皇帝御赐的。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_031", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "公司新来的实习生技术特别好，远超一般应届生的水平。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "他其实是竞争对手公司派来的商业间谍，目标是窃取核心技术资料。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_032", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "李明每天晚上都能听到楼上有弹珠声，但楼上没人住。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "楼上的空房里有一台被遗忘的发报机，弹珠声实际上是定时发送的信号。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_033", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王雪的闺蜜最近总是避着她接电话，神色慌张。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "闺蜜被一个诈骗团伙控制了，对方用她的家人安全威胁她做事。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_urban_034", "genre": "urban", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "赵峰在整理旧物时发现了一本存折，上面有一笔巨款是他不知道的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "存折是父亲生前偷偷存的，用来给他出国留学用的。父亲没来得及说就去世了。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
